21:25.160 --> 21:28.880
at, that are very natural and direct.

21:28.880 --> 21:32.880
In fact, at the technical level, we would say these are the ones that have a definite

21:32.880 --> 21:36.040
energy in their vibrations.

21:36.040 --> 21:42.240
