25:31.340 --> 25:36.100
and you find that the possible places you could find, the possible states you could find the

25:36.100 --> 25:39.980
electron wave function in, come in a discrete set.

25:39.980 --> 25:45.660
So again that discreteness is emergent because it's a property of the different solutions

25:45.660 --> 25:51.020
to the equation, in this case the Schrodinger equation rather than the equation for a string

25:51.020 --> 25:53.060
in a guitar.

25:53.060 --> 25:56.620
So that's where quanta come from.

25:56.620 --> 26:02.060
It's not because you pixelated the universe, it's because you solved an equation and the

26:02.060 --> 26:05.420
solutions come in a discrete set.

26:05.420 --> 26:11.220
