27:39.020 --> 27:43.620
The electric field has a value at every point in space.

27:43.620 --> 27:47.140
It's a little vector because the electric field is not just a number, it's a little

27:47.140 --> 27:51.420
arrow with a direction and a magnitude at every point in space.

