28:16.620 --> 28:21.260
point in space around you right now, including inside you for that matter, and also, you

28:21.260 --> 28:23.380
know, out in interstellar space.

28:23.380 --> 28:27.940
Every point in space has a value for the electric field and the magnetic field.

28:27.940 --> 28:29.540
That's what a field is.

28:29.540 --> 28:34.940
A field is an entity that takes a value at every point in space.

