28:37.860 --> 28:39.220
That would be a bad question to ask.

28:39.220 --> 28:42.700
I mean, you're welcome to ask it, but the answer is there isn't anything that the fields

28:42.700 --> 28:43.900
are made of.

28:43.900 --> 28:46.260
The world is going to be made of the fields, okay.

28:46.260 --> 28:50.740
The fields are the bottom layer of reality, according to quantum field theory.

28:50.740 --> 28:52.580
Now quantum field theory might not be the final answer.

28:52.580 --> 28:57.420
I'll leave it in gesture at the very end toward the idea that it's not the final answer.

28:57.420 --> 29:01.780
