30:02.660 --> 30:05.940
You know if you looked for these particles, whether you found the electron or proton, they're

30:05.940 --> 30:08.380
very different looking particles.

30:08.380 --> 30:14.860
When the phenomenon of entanglement tells you that the combined state of both particles

30:14.860 --> 30:21.700
is not a wave function for the electron and a wave function for the proton, it is a single

30:21.700 --> 30:28.500
wave function for the system that is made of the electron and the proton.

30:28.500 --> 30:31.060
In other words, there is only one wave function.

30:31.060 --> 30:34.500
Ultimately, it will be called the wave function of the universe because it actually includes

30:34.500 --> 30:36.340
the whole universe, not just these two particles.

30:36.340 --> 30:41.260
But for right now, it is a wave function of these two particles and it is a function

30:41.260 --> 30:43.940
of x1 and x2.

