that the force-carrying particles are massless, and there's this little mathematical trick

01:47:10.180 --> 01:47:15.340
you can do to show that massless particles always give rise to long-range forces, which

01:47:15.340 --> 01:47:18.980
it seems that you can, then we're stuck, right?

